    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, preserved in exemplary condition. This specimen has been maintained to an uncompromising standard, presenting in showroom-ready form both aesthetically and mechanically. It offers a rare opportunity for the sophisticated collector to acquire a vehicle that reflects the highest tier of automotive care. Every detail has been meticulously scrutinized to ensure it meets the expectations of the most demanding enthusiast. We invite you to experience this peerless example of engineering excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
