    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape. It\u2019s been kept in a climate-controlled garage and looks just as stunning as the day it was first driven\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found! It handles like an absolute dream and still has that fresh, new-car smell. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly pampered and is ready for a new home, this is the one for you. Come see it for yourself, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
