    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2011 997.2 Carrera S is a superlative example of the final generation of hydraulic-steering 911s. It features the 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), delivering 385hp through a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-equipped mechanical limited-slip differential. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and the Sport Chrono Package Plus, providing active engine mounts and optimized throttle mapping. Meticulously preserved, the vehicle shows zero paint meter variances and a pristine undercarriage. All preventative maintenance is current, including recent bore scoping and fluid analysis, confirming a powertrain in peak mechanical health. This is a true turn-key, investment-grade driver's car.",
